        <mxCell id="AmHnWrLBn0aIf1uc1pJm-74" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Requesitos Funcionais:&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,0,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;RF001:&lt;/b&gt; O sistema deve permitir que o usuário faça login.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,1,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;RF002:&lt;/b&gt; O sistema deve permitir o cadastro de novos lotes de insetos.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,2,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;RF003:&lt;/b&gt; O sistema deve registrar informações sobre a eclosão dos ovos de cada lote.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,3,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;RF004:&lt;/b&gt; O sistema deve permitir o monitoramento da temperatura e da umidade das estufas.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,4,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;RF005:&lt;/b&gt; O sistema deve registrar diariamente a alimentação de cada lote de insetos.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,5,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,5,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;RF006:&lt;/b&gt; O sistema deve exibir um painel de colheita e venda dos lotes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;4,6,0&quot;&gt;&lt;b data-path-to-node=&quot;4,6,0&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;0&quot;&gt;RF007:&lt;/b&gt; O sistema deve calcular automaticamente a média da temperatura registrada nos últimos 10 dias.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="350" width="340" x="-59.00333333333299" y="513.3333333333335" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
